In response to one of the most frequently asked questions on his website, “what makes you think it’s possible to end extreme poverty?”
Global Citizen said: “The way to get there will be long and difficult, sometimes we will fall and fail.
However, like the great civil rights and anti-apartheid movements before us, we will succeed because we are more powerful together.
